{"tid":137344,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖)之前比mk妹帶左去警署雙放養貓番黎喇!!","createTime":"2017-02-27T17:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T08:50:41.000Z","uid":51117,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09a980d18ce86f18069ac0a49ece5d410ce3b010","tid":137344,"uid":51117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T17:44:13.000Z","msg":"前排睇到個post 話有隻放養貓比人帶走去警署唔受理就放低係警署門口就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發現啲特徵地點中晒 我之前係屋企樓下見到個隻<br />\n小小擔心佢 不過上次見佢識捉老鼠 知佢都有番啲求生能力<br />\n<br />\n今晚番屋企比我見番佢!!!!<br />\n佢又爬緊樹 我即刻好興奮hello佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就跑過黎好嗲又反下肚又訓上我大脾 好sweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n路過既放狗呀姐就搭下嗲 原來佢係橋另一邊街市養既貓 原本主人諗住養佢捉老鼠<br />\n但佢浪子性格 鍾意做街童 成日過橋黎我住呢條邨<br />\n棟棟樓啲保安都認得佢 世界仔黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呀姐話之前有人帶佢番屋企養 佢都嬲豬 周圍抓野 結果都要放番走佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都識番屋企沖涼 所以好乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/28/013606_5a62041cb075958785f35ba6942ad2b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2F013606_5a62041cb075958785f35ba6942ad2b7.jpg&h=147a2fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3O5C7d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3O5C7d2.jpg&h=979cb23a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cdD8h0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cdD8h0.jpg&h=84c9289d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/69669nB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F69669nB.jpg&h=d67278f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2oxC3G1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2oxC3G1.jpg&h=2b39b758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSor9 啲相夜媽媽影 貓貓又郁 所以少少矇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢瞓左係到6,7分鐘 我都唔敢郁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後 佢就離開左繼續做佢既深夜街童<br />\n下次見到佢再為大家報導下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba55ea9af7012f93c83508ca8ddd497f13746898","tid":137344,"uid":8827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T17:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c639ecb24275c70c13c154bbde423181b1b4843","tid":137344,"uid":34325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T17:51:15.000Z","msg":"絲打ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340d07543f71e605e8c34a58745e42fd030f2f6a","tid":137344,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T17:56:57.000Z","msg":"叫個Mk 妹情何以堪呢？"},{"pid":"5dc7dcdbde201ac843093f65383fcbf6d814ec07","tid":137344,"uid":14046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac85144421419550d399eda466b80b58aaf693e","tid":137344,"uid":51117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫個Mk 妹情何以堪呢？</blockquote><br />\n隻貓太痴人 好易帶走 不過浪子呢家野 就係留唔住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實佢頸圈前面有個牌仔 寫住佢係放養貓 仲有佢真正主人個電話 正常都應該睇下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2455c6682861a6bee8d04167d86029092c22a047","tid":137344,"uid":53500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5535d924d53709844c7cd9f5c48c30b09dc5509","tid":137344,"uid":43987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b3bf3632dd37691daa990119fb06b8f570b66e","tid":137344,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:43:45.000Z","msg":"乜原來有呢種養法<br />\n夜媽媽就由佢爛街？"},{"pid":"c7510cd4bf348562c3f70582794f180fea6e709c","tid":137344,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:44:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ab5f8dea736ccffcb5a9751539587d5125f07ee","tid":137344,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42609f5b2ffdb9dfa9b2e3480e4af23b8281f207","tid":137344,"uid":59165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:49:40.000Z","msg":"同我隻貓好似 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家貓 但好野性 整爛哂成屋野 日日同大貓打交<br />\n食衫 乜都咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbb個時執返黎 個時佢自己爬左上樹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f952a74d68e9446cd8ac4a8ef4034b7efc5d9a9c","tid":137344,"uid":51117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜原來有呢種養法<br />\n夜媽媽就由佢爛街？</blockquote><br />\n我都唔熟放養係點<br />\n淨係知佢係街市啲檔養既 可能都唔理佢咁多 識番去就好"},{"pid":"b8ba0512f05fe09e6405a72a0e3171012f5d5b2f","tid":137344,"uid":51117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同我隻貓好似 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家貓 但好野性 整爛哂成屋野 日日同大貓打交<br />\n食衫 乜都咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbb個時執返黎 個時佢自己爬左上樹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲格似要野外生活咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁佢痴唔痴你 有無相睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1815e0ca7547eb46a2dbb53f4c3f962fcb08c4ad","tid":137344,"uid":16270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜原來有呢種養法<br />\n夜媽媽就由佢爛街？</blockquote><br />\n你唔係認為 全世界都高樓大廈 之後隻貓屈係幾百尺到養呀"},{"pid":"f9febfe1a5ff7d89a441d72ea4f5e90fc88daafc","tid":137344,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貓不嬲都係「野外」生活"},{"pid":"17b2c5ddc52feea0d2c22494dc45b1ef3f14ef01","tid":137344,"uid":18139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T19:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/28/034509_5ed5f374cd82fe5416abb319f2c9e5ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2F034509_5ed5f374cd82fe5416abb319f2c9e5ab.jpg&h=215ed25e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n剛剛都見到佢即刻想影相po上黎 點知就見到呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲同佢玩左一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35525eddeb558a5ebff7e8eb6cfaaa28af33c06e","tid":137344,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:53:21.000Z","msg":"佢野外生活開困佢喺屋企就算食得好訓得好都唔會開心<br />\n其實香港少啲虐待動物嘅人就算喺街生活都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7c9e04a968ae74b9e01e4047faaf577976092c","tid":137344,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T04:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢野外生活開困佢喺屋企就算食得好訓得好都唔會開心<br />\n其實香港少啲虐待動物嘅人就算喺街生活都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係多呢d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d565d8ca960b0f415c1e156f9cfba5caa81c5d2a","tid":137344,"uid":51117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/28/034509_5ed5f374cd82fe5416abb319f2c9e5ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2F034509_5ed5f374cd82fe5416abb319f2c9e5ab.jpg&h=215ed25e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n剛剛都見到佢即刻想影相po上黎 點知就見到呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲同佢玩左一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f130a02273d0ef2c4373b7e4a3e524aaa871b0c6","tid":137344,"uid":51117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢野外生活開困佢喺屋企就算食得好訓得好都唔會開心<br />\n其實香港少啲虐待動物嘅人就算喺街生活都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係多呢d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲人就覺得要保護動物 所以要困住佢 但啲所謂危險其實又係人為既 如果本身啲動物係無人既野外 都可以靠自己能力生活架啦 不過人係無處不在<br />\n<br />\n無得拗既 唔識諗呀1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0ede7278bd752537da345dfdd3dbcd3145041e","tid":137344,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:25:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢野外生活開困佢喺屋企就算食得好訓得好都唔會開心<br />\n其實香港少啲虐待動物嘅人就算喺街生活都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係多呢d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲人就覺得要保護動物 所以要困住佢 但啲所謂危險其實又係人為既 如果本身啲動物係無人既野外 都可以靠自己能力生活架啦 不過人係無處不在<br />\n<br />\n無得拗既 唔識諗呀1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喺邊到都有危險架啦，就算冇人虐待佢都重有車，流浪狗，喺純正大自然生活重難搞"},{"pid":"ff1746f0e730ce6ce7ad5017da8b349715797b6b","tid":137344,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:50:41.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball"}]}